 : \\\"hello\\\"\");\n        } finally {\n            RestAssured.reset();\n            server.stop(0);\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static Class<?> invokeGeneratedClassLookup(String className) {\n        return (Class<?>) InvokerHelper.invokeStaticMethod(Prettifier.class, \"class$\", className);\n    }\n\n    private static void sendJsonBody(HttpExchange exchange) throws IOException {\n        byte[] responseBytes = \"{\\\"message\\\":\\\"hello\\\",\\\"count\\\":1}\".getBytes(StandardCharsets.UTF_8);\n        exchange.getResponseHeaders().set(\"Content-Type\", \"application/json; charset=utf-8\");\n        exchange.sendResponseHeaders(HttpURLConnection.HTTP_OK, responseBytes.length);\n        try (OutputStream outputStream = exchange.getResponseBody()) {\n            outputStream.write(responseBytes);\n        } finally {\n            exchange.close();\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 831, "output": 1094, "cacheRead": 54784, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 56709, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1781039040609, "responseId": "resp_0c962416b488006e016a287fc146b08193871e0d97259d4ef8"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_qYWG46nU8cI4EbVpaRjq44Jr|fc_0c962416b488006e016a287fceddb88193869b903a5961a8f7", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 2523 bytes to tests/src/io.rest-assured/rest-assured/5.5.0/src/test/java/io_rest_assured/rest_assured/PrettifierTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1781039061972}]}
